# Personal scratch work — every day's working-folder is local-only,
# EXCEPT a README that anchors the folder so the directory shows up in
# the repo across pushes (useful when studying from multiple machines).
# State files and daily todos under progress/ ARE tracked.
# Shared curriculum lives in learning-syllabuses/.
progress/*/working-folder/*
!progress/*/working-folder/README.md
